Introduction

Holly Queen (Korean: 할리퀸; Japanese: ヒイラギの女王) is a girl group under Gain Entertainment that currently consists of four members: Juhee, Sunbi, Yerim and Suhyun. They debuted on December 15, 2016 with the single Closer.
